{"tid":1897732,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好羨慕身邊朋友, 唔駛返工, 唔駛養家, 都可以生活到","createTime":"2020-02-26T01:43:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T04:24:51.000Z","uid":126454,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"05152d8465d68205e8149f5a6536fc192a4d9fcb","tid":1897732,"uid":126454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T01:43:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我係家中大仔, 未拍拖, 打份牛工得25K, <br />\n家中除左我外就人人失業無工開,<br />\n好重壓力....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n身邊朋友, 佢大我6,7年, 都快40歲, 但可以唔駛返工, 唔駛俾家用<br />\n佢俾果1千幾百, 同我講叫俾家用!?<br />\n最令我羨慕係佢可以買野食野唔駛諗.....<br />\n佢成日覺得好慘, 呢個世界差左佢咁,<br />\n但其實我仲慘過佢....<br />\n<br />\n點解人生咁唔公平...</span>"},{"pid":"759feda61b0ac634595734380ccae28ea3507153","tid":1897732,"uid":54927,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T01:50:53.000Z","msg":"因為你係賤種公屋<br />\n你老豆老母做愛係，for fun無諗到帶你個賤種黎要負責。<br />\n多個人 多把口你就要交家用"},{"pid":"3e6df4b803fefb0011d47929e144187b3c966e33","tid":1897732,"uid":126454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"759feda61b0ac634595734380ccae28ea3507153","tid":1897732,"uid":54927,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T01:50:53.000Z","msg":"因為你係賤種公屋<br />\n你老豆老母做愛係，for fun無諗到帶你個賤種黎要負責。<br />\n多個人 多把口你就要交家用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T01:55:38.000Z","msg":"我好努力咁改變現況<br />\n不過都冇無乜用<br />\n負擔真係好重"},{"pid":"e88b15e42937fab334c884e57494e90c9fab09ec","tid":1897732,"uid":38033,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T01:59:15.000Z","msg":"三十幾先得兩萬幾，玩完喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fdf5214c2077a807317f72623e8b3b6c0b79899","tid":1897732,"uid":126454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e88b15e42937fab334c884e57494e90c9fab09ec","tid":1897732,"uid":38033,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-